<l>niṟaiyariyar maṉṉaḷiya reṉṉāteṉ kāma</l>
<l> maṟaiyiṟantu maṉṟu paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even the Lust (of women) transgresses its secrecy and appears in public, forgetting that they are too chaste and liberal (to be overcome by it).</l>
